クラス InterledgerProtocolErrorBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.interledger.ilp.InterledgerProtocolErrorBuilder

  • @Generated(value={"Immutables.generator","InterledgerProtocolError.AbstractInterledgerProtocolError"})
public final class InterledgerProtocolErrorBuilder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type AbstractInterledgerProtocolError. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    InterledgerProtocolErrorBuilder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
